    "body": "* docs: document `vim.pack` as preferred installation method\r\n  Nvim 0.12 is not nightly anymore.\r\n\r\n* docs: replace deprecated `set_log_level` with `vim.lsp.log.set_level`",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-31T15:26:20Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
